SUMMARY:Campus Culture & Climate Survey Report Listening Sessions: Staff
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['Office of Diversity'\, 'Equity'\, 'and Inclusi'
 ]\\nCategory: Meeting\\nVice President for Diversity\, Equity\, and Inclus
 ion Brooke Vick recently shared the results of Swarthmore’s Campus Cult
 ure & Climate Survey with our community. The survey captured student\,
  faculty\, and staff perspectives on living\, learning and working at Swar
 thmore — you can learn more and find the full report on the Campus Cli
 mate Survey website.What do you think about the survey findings? Do the
 y reflect your experience at the College? What would you like to see come
  out of this survey\, as we plan together for the future of Swarthmore?Me
 als for ALL in-person sessions are covered by the Office of DEI.If you can
 ’t make these sessions\, you can attend another one of the sessions lis
 ted on the Events page of the Campus Climate Survey website (please 
 log in with your Swarthmore credentials to view)\, share your input throug
 h our feedback form\, or email culturesurvey@swarthmore.edu. We look for
 ward to hearing from you!\\nDetails: https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?t
 rumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%3D1390047766
URL:https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%
 3D1390047766
CATEGORIES:Meeting
END:VEVENT
