SUMMARY:The Garnet Choir is touring the United Kingdom this May
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['College Advancement']\\nCategory: Performance\\
 nThe Garnet Choir is touring the United Kingdom this May. We invite our UK
  alumni to attend any of the following performances to hear the ensemble
 ’s current repertoire. The students would love to see you in the audienc
 e as they share their work with international listeners. Performance Sched
 ule: Saturday\, May 16 | 7:30 p.m. Performing with the Reading Bach Choir 
 at St. James's Church\, Sussex Gardens\, London (W2 3UD). Purchase tickets
  here for £15.00. A meet-and-greet will follow the performance\, with cho
 ir members and alumni continuing the evening at The Swan for those who wou
 ld like to join. Tuesday\, May 19 | 5:30 p.m. Evensong with Selwyn College
  Choir at Selwyn College Chapel\, Cambridge Wednesday\, May 20 | 5:30 p.m.
  Evensong at Ely Cathedral\, Ely Thursday\, May 21 | 1:00 p.m. Lunchtime C
 oncert at Ely Cathedral\, Ely There is no formal registration or fee requi
 red for these events\, except for the St. James's Church performance — s
 imply arrive and enjoy the music. Guests are more than welcome to attend\,
  so please feel free to bring family and friends along. We hope you can at
 tend and enjoy a performance during the Garnet Choir’s UK tour! Warmly\,
 Swarthmore College Alumni\\nDetails: https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?t
 rumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%3D1395463329
URL:https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%
 3D1395463329
CATEGORIES:Performance
END:VEVENT
