SUMMARY:Pilates with Cathy Raymond
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['Recreation & Wellness']\\nCategory: Recreation-
 General\\nPilates is a progressive system of exercises designed to stretch
 \, strengthen\, and balance both mind and body. Benefits include increased
  core strength\, better posture and balance skills\, more physical and men
