SUMMARY:Summer 2026 Workshop Series: Research Ready
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ["Provost's Office"\, 'Beyond The Classroom'\, 'D
 ivision of Student Affairs']\\nCategory: Lecture/Panel Discussion\\nTuesda
 ys and Thursdays in Sci 101 from 12-1:30pm. Lunch will be provided. Learn 
 how library resources like Zotero can support your success this summer. We
 'll cover practical ways to get organized and build stronger research skil
 ls. Whether you're part of a team or working solo\, you'll walk away with 
 new tools and strategies to try. Presented by Simon Elichko\, Social Scien
 ces & Data Librarian\, and Andrea Baruzzi\, STEM Librarian.\\nDetails: htt
 ps://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%3D1395
 671876
